{"tid":2327784,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"忠實藍絲李偲嫣離世 fb 4日前留最後帖文狠批梁頌恆諷刺黎智英","createTime":"2020-12-16T09:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T10:18:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e66e45bd21ee40804c64c8b659f3ec846f7f6af3","tid":2327784,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:42:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/CVMDNM2YDBFGHM664GOR4GUDSI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FCVMDNM2YDBFGHM664GOR4GUDSI%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=0fea81ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FCVMDNM2YDBFGHM664GOR4GUDSI%2F&h=1c16d90e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/CVMDNM2YDBFGHM664GOR4GUDSI/</a>"},{"pid":"0f599aa588a028fbe90eb4b1a053cef1d34f03f4","tid":2327784,"uid":143026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:46:39.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"f5818e61f726681402f8f2a45c336279a053cefa","tid":2327784,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:46:48.000Z","msg":"唔好哄我<br />\n我會開心架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1582e172c8025d4c8442ee58c0cca94d96464e6","tid":2327784,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/10/093716_a2fa7c4fd99d0383d2815761dd42c85d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F09%2F10%2F093716_a2fa7c4fd99d0383d2815761dd42c85d.gif&h=fc812b57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a708795123b90f7c98c45125281e854817ce404","tid":2327784,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e4969c19f42084b9f47f3f85b62c177327a5a297","tid":2327784,"uid":12171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GvWSfX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GvWSfX.jpg&h=f1ab597a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6eb4915d77ade4f1c86407fd96f6f9d52a8a0f97","tid":2327784,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"01消息：「藍營」名人李偲嫣送院不治 與新冠肺炎有關<br />\n今日下午網上傳出李偲嫣由救護車送院的消息，《香港01》向可靠消息證實，李偲嫣今日送院不治，終年56歲，兩個消息人士均證實李偲嫣離世與新冠肺炎有關。<br />\n<br />\n李偲嫣曾擔任「香港家長聯會」會長，為前香港管理專業協會李國寶中學家長教師會主席，亦曾擔任反同性變組織「反逆向歧視大聯盟」發言人。她亦曾擔任九龍社團聯會的婦女事務委員會委員。<br />\n<br />\n李偲嫣曾受聘於經民聯立法會議員梁美芬，擔任非全職顧問，就教育政策提供意見。<br />\n<br />\n李思嫣facebook最後留言為12月12日，帖文批評梁頌恒離開香港，到美國尋求庇護。<br />\n<br />\n帖文指：「美國確實係收容香港逃犯的天堂！真係一件好事！未來就要看這些罪犯的人生會有多精彩！哈哈！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2955512/org/9da0077545b4e5d433f424d63fb00475.jpg/UkUx3YS0JxlBjlNh7dPjnvbbcKQPTvjjPUTDMD1EwzA?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2955512%2Forg%2F9da0077545b4e5d433f424d63fb00475.jpg%2FUkUx3YS0JxlBjlNh7dPjnvbbcKQPTvjjPUTDMD1EwzA%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=457f058c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16474bacfbb2942f68145e352679f1d799cb29fb","tid":2327784,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:03:53.000Z","msg":"消息人士向《立場新聞》表示，「正義聯盟」發起人李偲嫣於博愛醫院離世，終年 56 歲。消息指，李偲嫣在武漢肺炎病毒測步檢測呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》向曾僱用李偲嫣作非全職顧問，就教育政策提供意見的建制派議員梁美芬查詢，她表現驚訝「吓？幾時嘅事？」之後稱會立即了解。<br />\n<br />\n李偲嫣近日較少公開露面，但 4 日前曾在個人 fb 發文，批評前青年新政召集人梁頌恆流亡美國，指「未來就要看這些罪犯的人生會有多精彩！」並加上標籤，「下一個是誰」。當日她又分享黎智英還柙的相片，加上標籤「#應有此報」、「#毒害香港」、「#支持國安法」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%8E%E5%81%B2%E5%AB%A3%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96-%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B4-56-%E6%AD%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F-%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2581%25B2%25E5%25AB%25A3%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E5%25B9%25B4-56-%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=e3078800\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F-%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2581%25B2%25E5%25AB%25A3%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E5%25B9%25B4-56-%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F&h=034bf3c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%8E%E5%81%B2%E5%AB%A3%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96-%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B4-56-%E6%AD%B2/</a>"},{"pid":"825382ebb41ede5b8b21eb53c2b9ba75e2f4ae0c","tid":2327784,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1fJJxij.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1fJJxij.gif&h=1e65c5cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0df7c9b374485ab3274b9feb3941305cd36174a8","tid":2327784,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"#應有此報"},{"pid":"369cd9205ea1535ab5bf6f9e74b10057679b2dee","tid":2327784,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:08:31.000Z","msg":"#應有此報<br />\n#毒害香港<br />\n#支持國安法"},{"pid":"95944b01e0ade2780020408a59a7027f39ccb5bc","tid":2327784,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:18:20.000Z","msg":"push"}],"pinned":{"pid":"6eb4915d77ade4f1c86407fd96f6f9d52a8a0f97","tid":2327784,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"01消息：「藍營」名人李偲嫣送院不治 與新冠肺炎有關<b